                        <b>How Servizee chooses its service provider & Specialist?</b>  <br />
                        <br />
                        We know our Service providers & Specialists from our years of association with them, additionally we do a thorough background check of our service provider & Specialists and collect their legitimate KYC documents like Aadhar Card, PAN card and other address proofs to assure rightful services with behavioral training. <br />
                        <br />
