                        <br />
                        Servizee ensures 99.00% ownership of the service undertaken to provide best service at your doorstep.<br />
                        <br />
                        <b>Our Process Flow?</b><br />
                        <br />
                        <ul style="font-size:14pt;">
                            <li>Customer/Users downloads our Servizee application from the Google play store.</li>

                            <li>Customer/Users needs to register on the app using its Full name, Email Address, Mobile number & Address and submit the information to Login.</li>

                            <li>Once confirmation & Login is done, customer can proceed to choose & request for a service directly or Make a Query.</li>

                            <li>Fill in required information of service customer needs and submits to confirm the service required with the nominal base fare payment via App.</li>

                            <li>We receive service request and then co-ordinate with the relevant Specialists or Service provider.</li>

                            <li>Our Specialists confirm to provide service and arrives at the stipulated time frame and finishes the service.</li>

                            <li>Customers click Job Done.</li>

                            <li>For instant spot booking, all our Specialists will reach at the Customers place within 2 hours from the time of booking.</li>
                        </ul>
